iscipleship/">Evangelism and Discipleship</a></li>	<li id="menu-item-8768" class="menu-item menu-item-type-post_type menu-item-object-page"><a href="https://www.proclaimanddefend.org/resources/sunday-school-and-childrens-ministry-curricula/">Children’s Ministries</a></li>	<li id="menu-item-8760" class="menu-item menu-item-type-post_type menu-item-object-page"><a href="https://www.proclaimanddefend.org/resources/chaplain-resources/">Chaplain Resources</a></li>	<li id="menu-item-8759" class="menu-item menu-item-type-post_type menu-item-object-page"><a href="https://www.proclaimanddefend.org/resources/church-supplies-and-resources/">Church Supplies</a></li>	<li id="menu-item-8758" class="menu-item menu-item-type-post_type menu-item-object-page"><a href="https://www.proclaimanddefend.org/resources/missionaries/">Missionaries</a></li>	<li id="menu-item-15598" class="menu-item menu-item-type-post_type menu-item-object-page"><a href="https://www.proclaimanddefend.org/baptist-history/">Baptist History</a></li>	<li id="menu-item-8756" class="menu-item menu-item-type-post_type menu-item-object-page"><a href="https://www.proclaimanddefend.org/resources/churches/">Churches</a></li>	<li id="menu-item-8757" class="menu-item menu-item-type-post_type menu-item-object-page"><a href="https://www.proclaimanddefend.org/resources/colleges-and-seminaries/">Colleges and Seminaries</a></li></ul></li><li class="menu-item fl-menu-search-item"><div class="fl-search-form fl-search-form-button fl-search-button-reveal fl-search-button-center fl-search-form-width-full">
